metadata.name: Ethereal Dreams
metadata.description:
Look up, look down, & look all around. You're right where you need to be. 

What you put into the universe has network effects, just like Ethereum. Your mindset bolsters your actions, your actions confirm your passion, your passion effects your friends, your friends become inspired, your friends take action, and so the cycle continues. 

Before there can be actions, there's a lifetime worth of dreams. Be bold and embrace your passion.
